1
00:00:07,100 --> 00:00:07,580
Good morning.
早上好.

2
00:00:07,680 --> 00:00:09,480
Morning. Is there any coffee?
早上好,有咖啡吗?

3
00:00:09,680 --> 00:00:10,980
Mm-hm. I just made it. 
Mm-hm.我刚煮好.

4
00:00:12,480 --> 00:00:13,480
Do you want a muffin?
你想要块松饼吗?

5
00:00:14,780 --> 00:00:16,580
No, thanks. I'll get something at work. 
不,谢谢. 我会在上班时吃点什么的.

6
00:00:21,880 --> 00:00:23,430
Do you want a cup, Nancy?
你想来杯咖啡吗,Nancy?

7
00:00:23,530 --> 00:00:24,680
Yes, please.
是的,请给我倒一杯.

8
00:00:25,980 --> 00:00:26,880
Is Beth awake?
Beth醒了吗?

9
00:00:27,380 --> 00:00:29,680
More or less. She'll be right down. 
差不多了.她马上就下来.

10
00:00:29,880 --> 00:00:31,680
I'm giving her a ride to school.
我要开车送她去学校.

11
00:00:32,180 --> 00:00:34,530
Very clever, Counselor Hobart. 
真聪明,Hobart律师.

12
00:00:34,580 --> 00:00:36,080
She will get out of bed for a lift.
为了坐你的车她会起床的.

13
00:00:36,880 --> 00:00:38,765
What is your day like?
你今天有何安排?

14
00:00:39,380 --> 00:00:41,580
I go to the office this morning. 
我上午去办公室.

15
00:00:41,980 --> 00:00:43,680
And I'm in court this afternoon. 
下午要出庭.

16
00:00:44,080 --> 00:00:46,380
I won't be home late -about 6:30. 
今天到家不会太晚  大概6:30.

17
00:00:46,680 --> 00:00:47,480
How about you?
你呢?

18
00:00:47,880 --> 00:00:49,580
Yvonne and I have a meeting with a client.
Yvonne和我约了一个客户见面.

19
00:00:49,680 --> 00:00:50,580
Which client?
哪个客户?

20
00:00:50,680 --> 00:00:51,480
Bill Collins. 
Bill Collins.

21
00:00:51,680 --> 00:00:53,180
We're almost finished with his condo. 
他那套公寓的装修设计我们快做完了.

22
00:00:53,580 --> 00:00:54,880
I'll show you pictures tonight.
我今晚会给你看图片.

23
00:00:56,580 --> 00:00:57,630
Do you want a muffin? 
你想要松饼吗?

24
00:00:57,880 --> 00:00:59,730
I will make you a muffin.
我给你弄一块. 

25
00:00:59,880 --> 00:01:01,300
No, no, no. This is fine. 
不不不,这就够了.

26
00:01:06,180 --> 00:01:08,220
Good morning, Beth.
早上好,Beth.

27
00:01:08,380 --> 00:01:09,075
Hi, honey. 
你好,宝贝.

28
00:01:09,820 --> 00:01:12,680
I'm very well this morning, thank you. 
我今天感觉不错,谢谢.

29
00:01:13,070 --> 00:01:14,130
Would you like a muffin? 
想来块松饼吗?

30
00:01:15,720 --> 00:01:16,780
Do you want some yogurt? 
要酸奶吗?

31
00:01:18,357 --> 00:01:20,115
-An egg?  -Mom!
-鸡蛋呢?  -妈妈！

32
00:01:20,380 --> 00:01:21,212
Eggs are good.
鸡蛋很不错.

33
00:01:21,570 --> 00:01:22,522
I'm not hungry.
我不饿.

34
00:01:22,880 --> 00:01:24,730
Beth, you really must eat something. 
Beth,你真的必须吃写些东西.

35
00:01:24,880 --> 00:01:25,892
How about some cereal?
来点儿麦片怎么样?

36
00:01:26,250 --> 00:01:27,780
Dad, make her stop.
爸爸,叫她别说了.

37
00:01:28,080 --> 00:01:33,336
Breakfast is the most important meal of the day. Bye.
早饭可是一天中最重要的一餐.再见.

38
00:01:33,960 --> 00:01:38,059
-Bye.   -Bye. See you tonight.
-再见.  -再见.晚上见.

39
00:01:38,650 --> 00:01:40,350
-Richard!  -Dad!
-Richard!  -爸爸!

40
00:01:41,480 --> 00:01:42,980
You were taking Beth to school!
你说过要送Beth去学校的.

41
00:01:44,480 --> 00:01:49,480
Oops! Well, then I will have a muffin.
Oops! Well,那我吃块松饼.

